    <title>
      <string language="en">Trigonometric Ratios and Reference Angles of General Angles</string>
    </title>
    <language>en</language>
    <description>
      <string language="en">This applets enables pupils to visualize what is the reference angle of any general angle in trigonometry. 
At the same time, it shows how to determine the trigonometric ratio of any general angle (between -1440 to 1440 degrees) 
through visualizing the appropriate reference triangles in a unit circle around the 4 quadrants.</string>
    </description>
